core-identity-username-value-generator.label: Standard username generator
core-identity-username-value-generator.help: The generator generates the user name based on the 'first name' and 'surname'. Generator deletes the diacritic, cuts first name and surname to a defined number of characters, and connects them with connection character.

connectioncharacter.label: Connection character
connectioncharacter.help: The character(s) to be used to connects the first name and surname. The value does not need to be filled in. In this case, the first name and surname will be connected without any coupling character.

firstnamecharactercount.label: Count of characters from the first name
firstnamecharactercount.help: The maximum count of characters to use from the fisrt name.

lastnamecharactercount.label: Count of characters from the surname
lastnamecharactercount.help: The maximum count of characters to use from the surname.

searchuniqueusername.label: Verify unique username
searchuniqueusername.help: The newly generated username will be searched. If username will be exists, numeric suffix will be added. Suffix may be incremented.

firstnamefirst.label: As first value use first name
firstnamefirst.help: When generating, the first name of the user will be added first. If you unchecked, the order will be the opposite.

core-identity-email-value-generator.label: Standard email generator
core-identity-email-value-generator.help: The generator generates the email adress based on the username. Adds a defined suffix to the username. Beware, the result value must match the correct email address format.

emailsuffix.label: Email suffix
emailsuffix.help: The Suffix will be added to the username and together they must create an email address.

connectioncharacter.label: Connection character
connectioncharacter.help: The character(s) to be used to connects the first name and surname. The value does not need to be filled in. In this case, the first name and surname will be connected without any coupling character.

firstnamecharactercount.label: Count of characters from the first name
firstnamecharactercount.help: The maximum count of characters to use from the fisrt name.

lastnamecharactercount.label: Count of characters from the surname
lastnamecharactercount.help: The maximum count of characters to use from the surname.

generatefromusername.label: Generate based on username
generatefromusername.help: Email will be based on existing username. The username must exist at the moment of generation.

firstnamefirst.label: As first value use first name
firstnamefirst.help: When generating, the first name of the user will be added first. If you unchecked, the order will be the opposite.

core-identity-script-value-generator.label: Scripted Generator
core-identity-script-value-generator.help: The generator executes the defined script. At the script input are these attributes 'entity' and 'valueGenerator'. Beware functionality 'value regenerate' must implement the script itself. The script must be from the system category.

core-identity-form-default-value-generat.label: Addition default values for the forms with next inforamtion
core-identity-form-default-value-generat.help: Generator add default values for all attributes.

formdefinitionuuid.label: Form
formdefinitionuuid.help: Form must be for given entity type (IdmIdentity). If you leave form empty, the values will be added to all form definition.

regexmultiplevalues.label: Separator
regexmultiplevalues.help: If the attribute is multi-valued and the default value contains multiple values, write character(s) that seperate values. If left blank, a default character will be used ','.

core-test-long-running-task.help: Counts to given count, waits 300ms for every iteration.
